title: Import of creamery butter in Canada 2017
summary: The Import of creamery in Canada during 2017 showed several fluctuations during the year .
The Import values have been displayed using Tonnes as unit of measurement .
The most relevant peaks have been recorded during the months of February and June .
gold: The graph describes the import of creamery butter ( in tonnes ) in Canada during 2017 . As can be seen from the graph , the value reports two significant peaks during the month of March and June . The minimum value has been recorded during the month of September .
